            "question_color": "#000000",
            "question_bg_color": "#ffffff",
            "answer_color": "#000000",
            "answer_bg_color": "#ffffff",
            "accordion_mode": true,
            "question_1": "What's in my kit?",
            "use_product_description_for_question_1": false,
            "answer_1": "<p>Every kit includes the [Brand] Sonic Whitening Device and a shade card. The Starter Kit adds 1 PAP+ gel syringe (~3 weeks), The System adds 2 with refills every 5 weeks, and the 90-Day Transformation adds 6 plus a travel case and [Brand] Purple Toothpaste.</p>",
            "question_2": "How long per session?",
            "answer_2": "<p>Ten minutes a day. Load the gel, bite down, and get on with getting ready — the device is hands-free. Rinse when you're done.</p>",
            "question_3": "Is PAP+ safe?",
            "answer_3": "<p>PAP has been used in Australian cosmetic whitening for years. It's a peroxide-free pathway that breaks down stains without free radicals — so you get the lift without the sting.</p>",
            "question_4": "How do I use it?",
            "answer_4": "<p>1. Load it — a ribbon of PAP+ gel in the tray. 2. Bite down — LED on, hands free. 3. Live your life — ten minutes while you do your makeup. Rinse. Done.</p>",
            "question_5": "Shipping & returns",
            "answer_5": "<p>Subscriptions always ship express, free. One-time orders ship free over $79 (the Starter Kit pays $9.95). Returns are covered by the Shade Card Guarantee: photograph Day 1 — if Day 30 isn't visibly whiter, we refund everything and you keep the device.</p>",
